Since David seems to have forgotten the thorough thrashing he got before
regarding the CPSR letter, here is a repost of the complete paper I did for
my philosophy class on his argument (I needed a good fallacious argument,
and lo and behold: David was there). I include the original relevant
articles since many here may not have seen them, either.

It is long, but informative. The meat is down in Parts 3 and 4 if you want 
to skip the dull stuff. The observant will note that David isn't doing 
what he said he would in several places.

Oh yes - I got an 'A'. :-)

